cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper is about image captioning, which is a task in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also involves natural language processing (cs.CL) as it generates captions in natural language. The use of deep learning models for this task also falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper involves the use of scene graphs, which are a type of visual representation, making it relevant to multimedia (cs.MM).
